name: Kristen Stewart
description:
Kristen Stewart (born April 9, 1990) is an American actress. She has received various accolades, including a British Academy Film Award and a César Award, in addition to nominations for an Academy Award and a Golden Globe Award.

Yes, this is my first TI.

That meeting with Kristen Stewart was still a teenage dream, so I wanted to give her the first TI.

This TI data set is taken between her 17-20 years old, yes, I like young ones.

*It is recommended to set the clip to 1.

If you have any questions, you can leave a message to me, and I will give feedback in time. :)
